    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> Sets the maximum number of messages sent to the destination per second. Use this output-rate-limiting functionality only when using disk-buffer as well to avoid the risk of losing messages. Specifying <userinput>0</userinput> or a lower value sets the output limit to unlimited.</para>
